excerpt: 'We propose a novel content-aware graph-based representation that can infer
suggestions for color palettes and color assignments to designers by
capturing the types of elements (e.g., text, background, decoration),
the associated colors, and the relationships between UI elements.
This allows dynamically suggesting color palette selection in re-
sponse to changes in color preferences and assigning updated colors
for UI elements by employing graph neural networks (GNNs)'
